		CloudWatch
================================================
	- Basic Monitoring
		-- Is Free
		-- Polls erery 5 minutes
		-- 10 metrics
		-- 5GB of data ingestion
		-- 5GB of data storage
	- Detailed Monitoring
		-- Is Chargeable
		-- Changed per instance per month
		-- Polls every minute
	
